Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直戴着那个发饰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么理由算是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是没啥理由啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记带数学的笔记了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天有数学课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的哦  不是还有作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家去取一趟  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正作业也没做  带不带都一样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍然是印尼语早安的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:05.13,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,300)\fad(600,200)}日\N常\N之\N9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了出现了出现了…麻衣老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这莫非就是必杀技之「招呼保留」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是大气非凡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像山一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  就像山一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…实际上是不是已经不止山的程度了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  和山是没有一丁点关系就是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  麻衣生气的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我昨天把麻衣便当里的西兰花吃了的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就买来啦  西兰花～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了后我才知道麻衣最喜欢西兰花了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后我一直觉得自己做了不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也不是西兰花的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜花？看来也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我做的错事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道她是为了哪件而生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我心里大概有数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就只能老实向她道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  昨天吃了你的主菜真对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了兔子苹果  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你的饭  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到只剩黑豆了  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为昨天午饭的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  莫非是更早之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把麻衣抽屉里放着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨像的头折断的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是之后擅自把佛像带回家的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是偷偷地把佛像埋进土里的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:03.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}便条：对不起  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是后来改变主意  在麻衣的桌子上供奉神像的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进一步想想  难道是丢进焚化炉里烧了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  麻衣你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么啊  原来是在听音乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你才会不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道  一个人在那里自言自语地说个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险  差点就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半部分的事  我第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  田中同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:07:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你的发型  是不是稍微违反了学校里的风纪规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃铜锣烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:15.54,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  还要写讲义  我全忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离数学课还有五分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天已经借美绪的作业抄过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一生的请求！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  果然就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀  忘记做数学作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就借我抄一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  Thanks  多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦  我会以超马赫速度抄完的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  超级大迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账东西  早上开始就在吵什么吵  正雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我超级大迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被裁员了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  那个  这个好像和数学讲义有些出入…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会请你喝果汁的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课迟到了  老爸也被裁员了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪一边都糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是做这种事的时候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样正雄岂不是糟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来正雄会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做这种事的时候啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是生死攸关的时候啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我讲义啦  麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这样了  我会请你吃车站前面的那个的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T…Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  这个  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这不是有的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点拿出来啦  麻衣个坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就以超快速度开抄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我的那张讲义  是什么时候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:22.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去新奥尔良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题  有没有会解的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有够难的啊  赤城的课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记做作业  就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答错问题的话  又会让他生气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我话讲在前面  没干劲的家伙们我会马上记录在成绩单上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这一招吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会就这么被你吓倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.05,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N11
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是23号  我就点座号23号的中之条…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手抽筋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这时候手抽筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  这样下去的话会进入他视野的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先逃向死角  向死角…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子  椅子被挪动了呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什么声音  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有谁的手机响了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信谢礼～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一幕哟  看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫做「全班笑得开了花」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个问题  相生你来回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！  咻啪啪啪啪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻啪啪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:04.02,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N12
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  砂糖和牛奶都买了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没有忘记买的东西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天的鸡蛋可真便宜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我也买了一堆呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了  今天是鸡蛋的特卖会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢  虽然还能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是回店里一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑猫先生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…我不能养你呢  都已经有博士在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  随便带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…但是好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才不是这个问题呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  难道不可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  可爱是可爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  喂养小动物就要费心去照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你办的到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会帮你哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫它的排泄物你也得做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃什么都不打算帮忙的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就不给你摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！  那…那可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了  不是那个问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士  博士  睡着了哦  这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔顺哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士好狡猾  我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子的毛也好柔顺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子两边也好柔顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边的肉球好柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边的也好柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴的毛也好柔顺！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起尾巴  它耳朵里面的毛才柔顺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  但是摸起来的感觉  尾巴更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴才不柔顺呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  是不是哪里痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了「说话围巾」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哆啦A梦哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士好厉害  但也太快了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快让阪本戴上看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫叫阪本吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  箱子上也这么写的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  真是廉价的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  戴上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就会说话了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会说话哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想  你们刚才都摸得太过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说  猫会叫个不停几乎都是因为肚子饿了的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  我不知道这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为箱子上写着「阪本」  这也太随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  我就说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都多少岁了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我8岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}名乃的制造年龄是1年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我1岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照人类的年龄来算的话可是有20岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫我「阪本先生」才对头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:18.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大阪腔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对头…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  以后能吃到免费的饭我是很感激啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过希望你们能够谨记对长辈的那份尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句  你们给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定抱有「因为是猫就能随便摸」这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可说清楚了  虽然我不讨厌被随便摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  猫有着自己的限度…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它放回原来那个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:53.82,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,270)\fad(600,0)}草\N\N\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我付了房租还给我吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有困难就要互相关照嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有别的需要的话  不要客气  直接说就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  稍微借我点钱…随便说说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}得意忘形的日文是「天狗になる」字面意思就是「变成天狗」…冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  稍微对你好点你就得意忘形了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:44.90,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)\bord10\shad0\be50\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}草\N人\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教…教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像误会什么了  校长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把它身体的部分打开来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:14.43,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,290)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N13
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我赢了的话  车站前的那个就作废了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁一局定胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready  GO…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  麻衣  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你是不是有点抢跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  确实是有点早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那样一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧   是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当做没看见  我们再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么重新摆好姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready  GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻视了对手的握力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  这样一来热身运动也做够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀  这可真是相当难缠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  但是我无论身心都开始热起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该动…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真格的了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我走神了  哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我居然连续三次大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  是是  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看到了  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初心者的好运就到此为止了哦  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地来决胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  这不是很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫扳手腕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我稍微保管一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好久没有拿出全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我差不多一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不认真的话  我也认真不起来了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  下次才是真真正正的决战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要使出必杀技了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个破扳手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变得那么热血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  我忘记去上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一趟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉一开始就不怎么对劲呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  车站前面的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和23瓶果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天手抽筋而且没有做讲义还被骂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  结果正雄他会怎样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道了啦  我再追加一瓶果汁给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解呢…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.45,-0:00:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳豆激酶这名  有没有让人想吐槽这是什么笑点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这激酶算什么啊  是小夜曲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:34.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(255,340)}Kinase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:34.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(436,340)}Serenade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下回的日常是第4话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.32,0:23:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
