Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:00.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是不是坠入爱河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:03.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小时满脑子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意识不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:08.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}觉得与平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:06.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}觉\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:09.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:13.52,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:12.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N情\N相\N悦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:15.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  视线和他对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什么什么  这种忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:25.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路乱成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:31.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那种事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感觉都要发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急转直下的我的爱慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眨眼间  脸像着火般变得通红
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:45.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怎怎怎么可能  我的手居然在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是所谓的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:50.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不不不不好了  说话咬到舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟糕的沉默  我语无伦次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想知道  你对我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:54.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}你\N对\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:58.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:01.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初恋！  在平日的上学路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:10.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}单单单单☆单相思
